@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.HasMinValue
Summary
  Specifies if the MinValue property is used.
Description
  Set HasMinValue to true to check the entered values in the control against the MinValue property.
  If the entered value is less than MinValue, it will be forced to be at least MinValue.
See Also
  <DELPHILINK TControl.Text>

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.HasMaxValue
