  Specifies if the MaxValue property is used.
Description
  Set HasMaxValue to true to check the entered values in the control against the MaxValue property.
  If the entered value is more than MaxValue, it will be forced to be no larger than MaxValue.
See Also
  <DELPHILINK TControl.Text>

